title: The Grateful Dead Live at Nassau Coliseum on 1991-03-29
lineage: MAC > Nakamichi CR-5A > Edirol FA-66 > Wavelab > R8Brain > TLH > FLAC 1644. Transfer by Andrew F. July 2011.
description:
Set 1

Feel Like A Stranger, Sugaree, Walkin' Blues, Dire Wolf, Me & My Uncle-> Mexicali Blues, Althea, When I Paint My Masterpiece

Set 2

Iko Iko, Saint Of Circumstance, New Speedway Boogie-> Truckin'-> Drums-> Jam-> The Other One-> Wharf Rat-> Throwing Stones-> Touch Of Grey, E: Brokedown Palace

reviews.review_text: We were there it was FUN! Just had a GRATE time! Appreciated the music for the date and loved the fact that it was still going on...just listen, you will love it too!  There's so much more, but not for here.
